chigan Math. J. 62 (2013), 691-703], as was pointed out by C.-C.\nLin et al., the approach used in the case $D=1$ can not be applied to the cases\n$D\\ge2$, which needs some new methodology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Feb 2017 01:40:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-03"}
